definition: one/1/single/a (article)/as soon as/entire/whole/all/throughout/"one" radical in Chinese characters (Kangxi radical 1)/also pr. [yao1] for greater clarity when spelling out numbers digit by digit
right/correct/couple/pair/towards/at/for/to face/opposite/to treat (sb a certain way)/to match together/to adjust/to fit/to suit/to answer/to reply/classifier: couple
couple who were made for each other

sentences.english: The upper port of the leg protective bag of the utility model is provided with a pair of fasteners.
sentences.chinese: 本实用新型护腿袋的上端口装有一对卡子。

sentences.english: The plow was pulled by a yoke of oxen.
sentences.chinese: 一对公牛同轭拉着一头犁。

sentences.english: In theory, ke- rose can be reduced to obtain a couple of sugar alcohols which are epimers and have the same molecular weight.
sentences.chinese: 酮糖被还原时理论上生成一对等量的差向异构体糖醇。

sentences.english: A dumb and a dumber will never make a good combination
sentences.chinese: 阿呆与阿瓜永远不会是一对好组合。

sentences.english: The social effect of an evening of one-on-one theatre is interesting.
sentences.chinese: 这一夜一对一剧场的社会反响很有意思。

sentences.english: Shorthand and typewriting have been described as the twin arts.
sentences.chinese: 速记和打字被说成是一对孪生技巧。

sentences.english: I showed him a wide selection, and quickly he picked out a pair.
sentences.chinese: 我给他展示了许多款选择，很快他选种了一对。

sentences.english: The prisoner had on his feet fetters weighing fifty pounds.
sentences.chinese: 这犯人的脚上有一对五十斤重的铁球。

sentences.english: I think David and Victoria Beckham are a perfect match.
sentences.chinese: 我认为戴维贝克汉夫妇真是天生一对。

sentences.english: Players may wear a pair of thick socks and lights, soft-soled running shoes.
sentences.chinese: 参加者可穿一对厚袜子及轻而鞋底较软的跑鞋。

sentences.english: How much is a pair of anti-reflection lenses?
sentences.chinese: 一对不反光镜片大约要多少钱？

sentences.english: A pair of lovers in Shichahai, yes…
sentences.chinese: 昨日，在什刹海，一对情侣在雪景中缠绵。

sentences.english: Larvae dark gray color, green or weak stomach abdomen only with three and a pair of tail foot.
sentences.chinese: 幼虫深灰绿或淡青色，腹部仅有腹足三对及尾足一对。

sentences.english: While a pair of hollow jacks without electrodes are correspondingly and additionally arranged on the lamp base.
sentences.chinese: 而在管座上对应地增设了一对不带电极的空心插孔。

sentences.english: The Ci poem writer Han Yuanji and his son Han Biao were effective litterateurs at Song dynasty.
sentences.chinese: 韩元吉和韩淲是南宋词坛的一对父子作家。

sentences.english: Pictured here: A couple walks through the Lavaux Vineyard Terraces along Lake Geneva in Switzerland.
sentences.chinese: 图为一对夫妇沿瑞士日内瓦湖在拉沃克斯葡萄园散步。
